Bottom navigation contains 3 nav elements: home, add, menu
    user click on home -> opens HomeScreen
    user click on menu -> opens MenuScreen
    user click on add -> sequentially one after the other appear fab buttons upside the bottom Bar
        if click on build item -> open buildScreen (coming with next version), now just paint it gray
        if click on gallery item -> opens bottomSheetFragment with grid layout images
        if click on scan item -> system intent to take photo, then open resultScreen
        if click on the other place -> sequentially one after the other disappear fab buttons